item.description:
Hi Ladies,

Please join me for lunch at the Ipswich Inn. We will have a special menu, and the prices are more than reasonable. There is a cozy room for us, with a fire place, comfy couches to lounge. Maybe even a Brandy, or wine, if your in the mood!

We can plan some events, I'll have my computer with me. I'd like to discuss setting some dates for herbal gardening, soap making, and anything you desire to schedule.

I'd like to get the Inn keeper a count by 3/28, If possible. After lunch, we can take a walk around some historic areas, if your up to it!

Laura

group.name: Women Supporting Women Through Life's Incredible Journeys

item.name: Ladies Luncheon - Beautiful Ipswich Inn!
